---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions" description="xConvert24.com terms and conditions of use — disclaimers, limitations of liability, and acceptable use." keywords="terms and conditions, terms of service, disclaimer, liability, acceptable use, xConvert24 terms">
  <div class="max-w-3xl prose dark:prose-invert prose-gray">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Terms and Conditions</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: June 2025</p>

    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      By accessing and using xConvert24.com ("the Website"), you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use the Website.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">1. Use of the Service</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">xConvert24.com provides free online unit conversion tools and calculators for personal, educational, and professional use. You may use the service for lawful purposes only.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">2. Accuracy Disclaimer</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      While we strive for accuracy, all conversion results are provided <strong>"as is"</strong> without warranty of any kind. You should not rely solely on our tools for critical applications including but not limited to:
    </p>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <li>Medical decisions or healthcare dosing</li>
      <li>Financial transactions or trading</li>
      <li>Engineering safety calculations</li>
      <li>Legal or regulatory compliance</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Always verify critical conversions using authoritative professional tools or certified instruments.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">3. Currency Rates</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      Currency conversion rates on this website are static reference approximations for estimation purposes only. They do not constitute financial advice and should not be used for actual monetary transactions. For live market rates, consult a licensed financial service provider.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      All content, design, code, and branding on xConvert24.com are the property of xConvert24.com unless otherwise stated. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from this content without express written permission.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, xConvert24.com and its operators shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of, or inability to use, the Website or its tools.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">6. Availability</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      We make no guarantee that the Website will be available at all times. We may modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of the service without notice.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">7. Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      The Website may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of any third-party websites.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">8. Prohibited Use</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">You agree not to:</p>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <li>Use automated scripts to scrape or overload the Website</li>
      <li>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to any part of the service</li>
      <li>Use the Website in any way that violates applicable laws</li>
      <li>Redistribute or resell the service as your own</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      We reserve the right to update these terms at any time. Continued use of the Website after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">10. Governing Law</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      These terms are governed by the laws of the jurisdiction in which the Website operators reside. Any disputes shall be resolved in the applicable courts of that jurisdiction.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Questions about these terms? Visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">contact page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
